title: When God Talks Back
description:
Shiobhan jumped into a slot that was freshly vacated and shared with me the experiences she has received. She notes early on that some churches don't like this kind of thing. Many people I talk to are looking or waiting for some sort of supernatural experience. She wasn't looking for it but it happens to her. How do we handle it? Do we value it? What do you think about it?  

If you want to study this I recommend T.M. Luhrmann's When God Talks Back. https://www.amazon.com/When-God-Talks-Back-Understanding-ebook/dp/B005IQZAQ0

For the audio podcast mirror on Podbean http://paulvanderklay.podbean.com/
